          "hydrochlorothiazide",
          "diabetes",
          "type 2 diabetes",
          "fasting blood glucose",
          "metformin",
          "Farxiga"
        ]
      },
      {
        "heading": "Clinical Note",
        "section_value": "Patient likes to travel and is planning a trip to Columbus, Georgia in the next month or so. She is part of the Lion's Club.\nMEDICATIONS\nPatient reports that she is taking amlodipine, lisinopril 20 mg once daily, hydrochlorothiazide, Metformin, and Farxiga.\nREVIEW OF SYSTEMS\nMusculoskeletal: Reports left knee pain and instability,\nVITALS\nTemperature: 98.2 degrees F\nHeart rate: 72 bpm\nRespirations: 16\nBlood pressure: 122/70 mmHg",
        "medical_concepts": [
          "amlodipine",
          "lisinopril",
          "hydrochlorothiazide",
          "metformin",
          "Farxiga",
          "left knee pain",
          "knee instability",
          "temperature",
